        {
            "title": "反覆向好 滬指收升3點 深指0.7 % 芯片與貴金屬股各領風騷",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市午後走勢略呈反覆，滬市臨尾曾倒跌，深市則升幅收窄。芯片股反彈動力增加，中芯(00981)與華虹(01347)的A股均升超過4%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_00981-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指低開10點、報4103點便見全日低位，數分鐘後開始倒升，早市最高曾見4135點，漲22點，其後升幅收窄，午市中段一度挑戰早市高位但無功而回，指數進入下降軌，尾市轉為好淡爭持；滬指最後收報4116點，升3點或0.08%，成交降至1.18萬億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指重新跑贏，同樣甫開市便是全日低位，報14102點，僅跌53，開市數分鐘便步入倒升之路，約於上午10時升幅已擴大至過百點，最高報14320點，漲165點，其後於高位橫行，升幅一直維持在75點以上；深指收報14255點，升99點或0.7%，成交亦減少至1.42萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數升4點或0.09%，以4723點收市；創業板指數升幅收窄至17點或0.54%，報3295點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-12.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-12.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">昨天弱勢的芯片股，今早已見明顯反彈，不少於午後更上層樓。中芯國際A股(688981.SH)漲4.1%，報127.19元；華虹(01347)A股(688347.SH)升4.74%，報139.52元；兆易創新(03986)A股(603986.SH)升5.36%，報307.65元；納芯微(02676)A股(688052.SH)更飆6.17%，報185.22元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">不過，AI芯片概念股寒武紀(688256.SH)升幅卻收窄至0.81%，報1353.87元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：赤峰黃金官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_Chifeng-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：赤峰黃金官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_Chifeng-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：赤峰黃金官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另一邊廂，金價再創新高，貴金屬板塊再度炒上。湖南白銀(002716.SZ)與白銀有色(601212.SH)等於早市已相繼漲停板。在A+H股份中，赤峰黃金(06693)A股(600988.SH)午後也曾升約10%短暫封板，收報38.39元，升9.81%；山東黃金(01787)A股(600547.SH)升8.2%，報51.47元；紫金礦業(02899)A股(601899.SH)也升2.2%，報38.13元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15600148-%e5%8f%8d%e8%a6%86%e5%90%91%e5%a5%bd-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%873%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%870-7-%e8%8a%af%e7%89%87%e8%88%87%e8%b2%b4%e9%87%91%e5%b1%ac%e8%82%a1%e5%90%84%e9%a0%98%e9%a2%a8",
